data.description: ***MULTIPLE OFFERS RECEIVED. SELLERS ARE CALLING FOR HIGHEST & BEST ON SUNDAY 2/11 AT 2:30PM*** Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home that offers a fantastic blend of comfort, style, and convenience. As you enter, you'll immediately notice the warm and inviting ambiance, thanks to the beautiful hardwood floors that grace the living areas. The living room is bathed in natural light, providing an ideal setting for relaxation or social gatherings. The well-appointed kitchen comes complete with modern appliances and ample cabinet space, simplifying meal preparation. Adjacent to the kitchen, a cozy dining area is perfect for enjoying meals. The three spacious bedrooms offer plenty of room and the bathroom is thoughtfully designed to provide comfort and functionality. Step outside to discover your own private sanctuary – a generously sized, fully fenced backyard with a charming patio area for outdoor dining and entertaining.
